Love MOD! You can make your own, or you can do one of their recommended pizzas! All the pizzas they share the calorie content AND the nutrition facts are on MyFitnessPal too. 11/10. 

You can do all the MODifications you want with no extra charges. 

This location is very easy to get to too. Anything inside a mall makes me cringe, I feel you, but the restaurant is literally right next to the parking lot. I park, take 15 steps, I'm in, I'm out.